 border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">SESSION_RESTARTED</span><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-3 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">MEMORY_CORRUPTION</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-8 mb-8\"><div><div class=\"font-[Creepster] text-3xl text-primary\">38</div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Confirmed Theories</div></div><div><div class=\"font-[Creepster] text-3xl text-primary\">12</div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Unverified</div></div><div><div class=\"font-[Creepster] text-3xl text-primary\">3</div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Corrupted</div></div></div><h1 class=\"font-[Creepster] text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-primary mb-2\">The Freak Circus Theories,<br/>Timeline Analysis &amp; Hidden Lore</h1><p class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-6\">Every Route Hides Another Theory</p><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-lg max-w-2xl mb-8\">Explore timeline corruption, hidden motives, replay anomalies, and community investigations inside The Freak Circus archive.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4\"><a class=\"px-6 py-3 border border-primary text-primary hover:bg-primary hover:text-surface transition-colors font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-sm uppercase\" href=\"#archive\">Explore All Theories</a><a class=\"px-6 py-3 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-sm uppercase\" href=\"#timeline\">Investigate Timeline Anomalies</a></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-surface py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-8\">Evidence Wall // TOP SECRET</div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-4\"><a class=\"block bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors group\" href=\"#pierrot-loop\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-2\">search</div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-2xl text-primary mb-1\">T_04</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-2\">Pierrot Loop</div></a><a class=\"block bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors group\" href=\"#doctor-aware\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-2\">search</div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-2xl text-primary mb-1\">T_11</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-2\">Doctor Aware?</div></a><a class=\"block bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors group\" href=\"#memory-glitch\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-2\">search</div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-2xl text-primary mb-1\">T_07</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-2\">Memory Glitch</div></a><a class=\"block bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors group\" href=\"#null-route\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-2\">search</div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-2xl text-primary mb-1\">T_15</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-2\">Null Route</div></a><a class=\"block bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors group\" href=\"#mask-theory\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-2\">help</div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-2xl text-primary mb-1\">T_22</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-2\">Mask Theory</div></a><a class=\"block bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors group\" href=\"#corrupted\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-2\">help</div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-2xl text-primary mb-1\">T_??</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-2\">Corrupted</div></a></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-surface py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-8\">// Archive Indexing System</div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-3\"><a class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-outline/20 text-on-surface-variant hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs uppercase\" href=\"#by-topic\">By topic</a><a class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-outline/20 text-on-surface-variant hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs uppercase\" href=\"#by-character\">By character</a><a class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-outline/20 text-on-surface-variant hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs uppercase\" href=\"#by-credibility\">By credibility</a><a class=\"px-4 py-2 border border-outline/20 text-on-surface-variant hover:border-primary hover:text-primary transition-colors font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs uppercase\" href=\"#by-awareness\">By awareness</a></div></div></section><section id=\"featured\" class=\"bg-surface py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-4\">// Featured Investigation — This Week</div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-primary text-primary\">COMMUNITY CONFIDENCE: 78%</span></div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary mb-2\">THEORY_14 — META THEORY</div><h2 class=\"font-[Creepster] text-3xl md:text-5xl text-primary mb-4\">The Circus Does Not Exist</h2><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant mb-8 max-w-2xl\">Some players believe the circus is not a physical location, but a fragmented psychological space shared across collapsing timelines.</p><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-8\"><div><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-4\">Supporting Clues</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-on-surface-variant\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-primary\">■</span><span>Repeated impossible architecture between scenes</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-primary\">■</span><span>Inconsistent room layouts across playthroughs</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-primary\">■</span><span>Conflicting memories expressed by characters</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"text-primary\">■</span><span>Timeline-aware dialogue referencing unseen events</span></li></ul><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Architecture</span><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Timeline</span><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Psychology</span><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">Meta</span></div></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-4\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-2\">Screenshot A</div><div class=\"font-[Creepster] text-4xl text-primary/30 text-center py-8\">ROOM_A_v1.04</div></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-4\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-2\">Screenshot B</div><div class=\"font-[Creepster] text-4xl text-primary/30 text-center py-8\">ROOM_A_v2.01</div></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-6\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-2\">Hidden Dialogue Fragment</div><blockquote class=\"text-on-surface-variant italic border-l-2 border-primary pl-4\">&quot;This room... it was different before. Or maybe I am the one who changed.&quot;<footer class=\"text-sm mt-2 not-italic\">— Columbina, Scene 12 (3rd loop)</footer></blockquote></div></div></div></section><section id=\"archive\" class=\"bg-surface py-16 px-4 md:px-16 border-t border-outline/10\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-4\">All Freak Circus Theories</h2><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-8\">12 major community theories with confidence scores, evidence ratings, and community support</p><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary\">THEORY_07</div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-primary text-primary\">Community Accepted</div></div><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-1\">Pierrot Remembers Every Loop</h3><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-3\">Timeline Theory</div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-3 mb-4\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center mb-2\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Confidence Score</span><span class=\"font-[Creepster] text-xl text-primary\">82<!-- -->%</span></div><div class=\"w-full bg-outline/20 h-1 mb-3\"><div class=\"bg-primary h-1\" style=\"width:82%\"></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-2 text-xs\"><div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant mb-1\">Evidence</div><div class=\"flex gap-1\"><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span></div></div><div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant mb-1\">Contradictions</div><div class=\"flex gap-1\"><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-outline/30\">★</span></div></div><div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant mb-1\">Community</div><div class=\"flex gap-1\"><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-outline/30\">★</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 mb-4\"><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Character</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Pierrot</div></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Type</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Replay-Based</div></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Scenes</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">12</div></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Category</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Timeline Theory</div></div></div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-4\">Evidence suggests Pierrot reacts differently after repeated failed endings, retaining knowledge across timelines. On the 4th playthrough, he references choices from previous routes that the player never selected in the current save. Counter value at offset 0x4A20 affects his dialogue options.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">#<!-- -->Obsession</span><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">#<!-- -->Replay Awareness</span><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">#<!-- -->Narrative Corruption</span></div></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary\">THEORY_11</div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-blood text-blood\">Controversial</div></div><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-1\">The Doctor Is The Observer</h3><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-3\">Character Theory</div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-3 mb-4\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center mb-2\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Confidence Score</span><span class=\"font-[Creepster] text-xl text-primary\">67<!-- -->%</span></div><div class=\"w-full bg-outline/20 h-1 mb-3\"><div class=\"bg-primary h-1\" style=\"width:67%\"></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-2 text-xs\"><div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant mb-1\">Evidence</div><div class=\"flex gap-1\"><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-outline/30\">★</span></div></div><div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant mb-1\">Contradictions</div><div class=\"flex gap-1\"><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-outline/30\">★</span><span class=\"text-outline/30\">★</span></div></div><div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant mb-1\">Community</div><div class=\"flex gap-1\"><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-outline/30\">★</span><span class=\"text-outline/30\">★</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 mb-4\"><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Character</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">The Doctor</div></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Type</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Save Awareness</div></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Scenes</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">8</div></div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Category</div><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-sm font-bold text-foreground\">Character Theory</div></div></div><p class=\"text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-4\">The Doctor may be aware of the player directly, breaking the fourth wall through clinical observations. His Scene 7 description of the White Room ending matches unused files found in build 1.04. Some theorists believe he represents the game&#x27;s developer consciousness within the narrative.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">#<!-- -->Meta</span><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">#<!-- -->Fourth Wall</span><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-outline/30 text-on-surface-variant\">#<!-- -->Manipulation</span></div></div><div class=\"bg-surface-container border border-outline/20 p-6 hover:border-primary transition-colors\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-start mb-2\"><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-primary\">THEORY_09</div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs px-2 py-1 border border-primary text-primary\">Community Accepted</div></div><h3 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-lg font-bold text-foreground mb-1\">Columbina&#x27;s Memory Is The Key</h3><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant mb-3\">Memory Theory</div><div class=\"bg-surface border border-outline/20 p-3 mb-4\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center mb-2\"><span class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs text-on-surface-variant\">Confidence Score</span><span class=\"font-[Creepster] text-xl text-primary\">78<!-- -->%</span></div><div class=\"w-full bg-outline/20 h-1 mb-3\"><div class=\"bg-primary h-1\" style=\"width:78%\"></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-2 text-xs\"><div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant mb-1\">Evidence</div><div class=\"flex gap-1\"><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-outline/30\">★</span></div></div><div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant mb-1\">Contradictions</div><div class=\"flex gap-1\"><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-outline/30\">★</span></div></div><div><div class=\"text-on-surface-variant mb-1\">Community</div><div class=\"flex gap-1\"><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-primary\">★</span><span class=\"text-outline/3